            <title>Version 0.1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 23:30:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul><li>The Play button now responds the moment you click it, with a clear loading indicator while your game starts up.</li><li>Corvus Arcade steps out of the way only once your game is actually on screen, and comes right back when you close it.</li><li>Fewer permission pop-ups when you launch a game.</li><li>Smoother play, with fewer interruptions after your Mac tidies up temporary files.</li></ul>]]></description>
